The Chronicle Prosper Ndlovu in Dubai, UAE THE country’s vast infrastructure develoment opportunities are under spotlight at the on-going Zimbabwe Dubai Tourism and Infrastructure Investment Conference here in the United Arab Emirates. <img class="wp-image-593855 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-7.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-7.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-7-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Delegates follow proceedings Effective access and communication are critical enablers in the develoment of a thriving tourism industry hence today’s session seeks to highlight the state of the transport sector and profiling its various opportunities. <img class="wp-image-593854 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-8.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-8.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-8-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Delegates follow proceedings Deputy Minister of Transport and Infrastructural Development, Cde Mike Madiro, has delivered his opening remarks to the session in which he outlined key policy issues and the broader focus areas that local and foreign investors can tap into. <img class="wp-image-593851 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-9.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-9.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-9-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Delegates follow proceedings The conference is being hosted on the sidelines of the world acclaimed Expo 2020 Dubai, where Zimbabwe is participating in the opportunities district. <img class="wp-image-593849 size-full" src="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-10.jpg" alt="" width="680" height="380" srcset="https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-10.jpg 680w, https://www.chronicle.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2022/03/Dubai-10-360x200.jpg 360w" sizes="(max-width: 680px) 100vw, 680px" /> Delegates follow proceedings …more to follow    